name: Tumblr - Logo - OUAT
description: Replaces the regular Tumblr logo with the Once Upon a Time logo
additional_info: Tumblr Post if you want to share: [x] 10/31/2014 - Updated to fit new Dashboard layout 4/8/2015 - Updated to work with new header layout
css: @-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.tumblr.com"), url-prefix("https://www.tumblr.com") { .logo .logo-anchor:before { content: " " !important; } .logo .logo-anchor { height: 52px !important; width: 156px !important; margin: 0px 30px!important; display: block !important; background-size: auto 52px !important; background-image: url(https://static.tumblr.com/gwc9rra/FLKndnq8e/logo-ouat.png) !important; } svg.svg-logo, .logo .png-logo, .logo .preload-container { display: none !important; } }
